org.ObjectLayout.intrinsifiable

Class StructuredArrayIntrinsifiableBase<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.ObjectLayout.intrinsifiable.StructuredArrayIntrinsifiableBase<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T -
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    StructuredArray

    public abstract class StructuredArrayIntrinsifiableBase<T>
extends java.lang.Object
    This class contains the intrinsifiable portions of StructuredArray behavior. JDK implementations that choose to intrinsify StructuredArray are expected to replace the implementation of this base class.
